item.title: Announcing the Winners of the UN-aligned Photo Competition
item.description:
We would like to say thank you to everyone who took part in our Photo Competition! There were many fantastic entries with some awesome inspiring photography. As per rule of the contest, we have selected two winners.

1st Prize Winner: Anwar Sadat Swaka

In the streets of kibera, normal daily life goes on. Mama Maria as she is popularly known because of her daily religious attire, confidently makes her way.
